The paper discusses security challenges in IoT systems and proposes the use of machine learning and deep learning methods to enhance security. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of ML/DL methods, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the various components involved in IoT systems, which suggests that it could belong to cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Finally, the paper discusses the challenges involved in applying ML/DL to IoT security, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.SE (Software Engineering).
